high_descs: Hang a right to reach the sink.
Pick up the sponge to the right of the sink.
Rinse the sponge in the sink, removing it afterwards.
Turn to face the cabinets to the right of the sink.
Set the sponge down in the lower cabinet on the lefthand side where the soap is.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a sponge to set next to a bar of soap in a cabinet.

high_descs: Turn left and walk until you're almost to the door then turn left and walk to the counter to the right of the sink.
Pick up the sponge that's in front of you to the right of the sink.
Take a step to your left.
Get the sponge wet in the sink and then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Take a big step back to give yourself room to use the cupboards under the sink.
Open the second cupboard from the right and put the sponge in there before closing the door again.
anns.task_desc: Put a wet sponge in the cupboard.

high_descs: turn left and walk over to the bathroom counter on the left side of the room to the right of the sink
grab a sponge off of the counter top there
move to the left a bit and face the bathroom sink
place the sponge inside of the sink and rinse it off, then take it back out
turn around to back up a bit, and then face the sink cabinets again
place the sponge inside of a cabinet to the bottom right of the sink
anns.task_desc: place a clean sponge inside of the cabinet
